":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T02:35:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be0dec2738c03733a2420dc672f871293ecca397","tid":1007801,"uid":16453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T03:15:05.000Z","msg":"中國人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e8f101f60d3f262ae1e382c0d584b221dde9387","tid":1007801,"uid":57376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T03:22:42.000Z","msg":"咁撚想扮無事<br />\n通車算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n反正就算死咗人都可以賴哩樣賴果樣<br />\n唔好再扮到有監察啦<br />\n我寧願香港基建日日有大獲野<br />\n等班港豬無得食安樂茶飯<br />\n好過宜家日日陪佢地自我催眠扮無事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8830aae59f3216acb7c82c203fa894813dc50080","tid":1007801,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T03:22:53.000Z","msg":"【專訪】廿年前公屋短樁　今天沙中綫醜聞　楊德忠眼中的香港工程界隱患<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1009075\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1009075</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"c46adafb35400c818ac1924ddef7aac5e60ad12c","tid":1007801,"uid":55851,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T03:52:30.000Z","msg":"港鐵極高層勢力=中共太子黨"},{"pid":"229af6c572df7a168c7d7e7bfeb951bb503d21dd","tid":1007801,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T04:21:50.000Z","msg":"馬屎？"},{"pid":"0404460ee35fb8e2bc727a09a81534198724e946","tid":1007801,"uid":34760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5bb9090749c41813942bb24da3536e06833d8725","tid":1007801,"uid":32722,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T04:51:59.000Z","msg":"而家個狀況係政府主動篤鳩港鐵，但又唔肯召喚商業罪案調查科，情況有點怪<br />\n政府好小可做攪屎棍，唔通想借呢單野玩CY？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T04:25:24.000Z","msg":"政府想而家搞完一大輪就clo